Nunn-Regg student. He was real nice. And we had to 
share the room. And I had the top bunk and he had the

08:10.123 --> 08:12.868
lower bunk. and uh he was uh how old was he he must 
have been uh oh about 24. no he was a veteran also i

08:13.996 --> 08:40.813
don't know i don't recall that he was but he was not 
in the corps and he was getting his degree in

08:13.996 --> 08:40.813
accounting did you eat in the in the sabisa then uh 
no oh I, you see, the MSC had a place to eat, and I

