09:15.849 --> 09:16.570
Kyle Field. Yes, sir. Do you remember who the 
speaker was? No, sir. Most of us don't remember who

09:20.055 --> 09:21.958
the speaker was. Who came? What family came for 
your commencement? My mother and two of my

09:27.887 --> 09:31.792
sisters. That was all. And then, of course, Rachel 
was there. And I remember her. When I went across

09:40.126 --> 09:49.619
the platform to get there, my sister said, that's 
my daddy.

