his name was Don Harrison, and he used to work at a

09:49.639 --> 10:00.695
parts department with me. He was old. And he had two 
brothers that owned a clothing store. in San

10:08.729 --> 10:13.774
Antonio called Fomby's, and it stood for men. And 
