hey, all this is no good. Get it out and prove 
anything. So I just, I can't think of this

30:06.043 --> 30:14.633
chairman's name. He's an attorney. In Houston. He 
got out. He resigned. Otherwise, you couldn't

30:19.619 --> 30:22.542
imagine what was going on. So my wife, knows a lot of 
